<div class="node__content__right"><h2 class="node__title"><a href="/blog/the-scientific-fundamentalist/201101/beautiful-people-have-more-daughters">Beautiful People Have More Daughters</a></h2><div class="field field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
        <div class="field__item">Physically more attractive parents are more likely to have daughters than physically less attractive parents, both in the United States and in the United Kingdom.</div>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>


</div>
